title: Essential Slick - Richard Dallaway and Jonathan Ferguson [scala]
description:
Slick is a functional library for accessing databases from Scala. 
http://slick.lightbend.com/

As far as I know, this is currently the only book about Slick 3.0.

You can check out source code of examples from book: 
https://github.com/underscoreio/essential-slick-code

formats: pdf, html, epub

Buy it if You like it! 
http://underscore.io/books/essential-slick/

PS. book for previous version of Slick, 2.0, is included too
